"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:08:38.000Z","msg":"呢隻長期用唔係咁好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:40:25.000Z","msg":"洗一次已斷尾！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:41:57.000Z","msg":"我唔得 要長期用 不過無用好耐"},{"pid":"7b30a5aa490beb95e14a12df0b91e5a944b1eaa1","tid":621152,"uid":51717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"80f51d5d336f63bf05b24ff3eec82f2b91774a86","tid":621152,"uid":32887,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:54:17.000Z","msg":"我曾經同你一樣 晚晚洗兩三次頭都勁多頭皮  最辛苦都唔係頭皮 係痕到仆街 又多油 上網爬左好多文 發現好多人推薦大陸一隻叫康王復方酮康既產品 果陣真係太辛苦 抱住死馬當活醫既心態 好衝動咁係淘寶買左支黎試下  屌 用左兩次已經明顯好左勁多 一個月已經完全好晒 之後keep住每星期用一次 用左半枝左右 到而家半年無用過 都無番發既現像<br />\n認真 唔係話吹奏大陸產品 但如果真係好難頂 買枝番黎試下 可能真係幫到你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:50:33.000Z","msg":"唔係話大陸嘢一定無效，最重要係無監管。大家都知濕疹用類固醇會好見效，但唔可以長用，因為有嚴重後遺症。<br />\n大陸嘢無監管，撞到用猛藥禁藥當然好快見效，但對後遺症隻字唔提，最後奶嘢係你自己。<br />\n好多年前一隻減肥中藥，用咗隻超級利尿中藥，一食勁瀉水，體重一定減輕，啲人就話好見效keep 住食，結果食到腎功能衰竭，要終身洗腎。<br />\n仲用唔用，自己衝量。"},{"pid":"89b4d583031e443a61ddd46a534f985eaab5fbea","tid":621152,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ab9aa6455e37e418ea23529d910302ab8c89916","tid":621152,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"ccec7b19477b2d7865f4c39462257244403111ac","tid":621152,"uid":52576,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"87ae09318d8dba8790a4f2f99c045d20da6192f2","tid":621152,"uid":167905,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T06:41:00.000Z","msg":"番大陸買隻叫 復方酮康唑髮用洗劑 keep住兩日用一次會好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:12:58.000Z","msg":"呢個真係好有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:16:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/22787269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F22787269&d=dkkLZikCC5jk9TNU3iTsbDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=39d98e04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/22787269</a><br />\n<br />\n长期使用复方酮康唑发用洗剂会有什么后果？<br />\n<br />\n好似有類固醇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:54:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母殘體狗"},{"pid":"1965a74f7716474c4c0fad8886995e7713da7011","tid":621152,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:56:09.000Z","msg":"用咩洗頭水, 護髮素先?"},{"pid":"74752a003b52fb1586204d093112d50ab7468fc4","tid":621152,"uid":179104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:57:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa5b6f4539c4c1f70f6dfc3ea6a71376a86b1e73","tid":621152,"uid":12697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78cdc640c12669910a0c917a0c8ac9bea3fc8469","tid":621152,"uid":33130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e38cf651a95b09d12e5404fe54f65f31b2f6d45","tid":621152,"uid":12412,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T06:09:43.000Z","msg":"試咗施巴先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T08:11:21.000Z","msg":"我之前都係用其他大牌子洗完頭都會有頭皮<br />\n<br />\n自己就油性髮質 (出大半日街已經&ldquo;立&rdquo;哂)<br />\n用左施巴油性專用嗰隻就好返哂<br />\n<br />\n但一旅行用其他雜嘜都會痕+頭皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:00:17.000Z","msg":"Me three.. 由中學開始啲頭皮就好勁，尤其轉天氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用過head &amp; shoulder, 瀟灑, body shop, neutrogena..<br />\n隻隻都有用但用唔長，H &amp; S 用得耐會lup, 瀟灑用脫髮嚴重咗，body shop 其實幾好但有矽，neutrogena 唔再出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一年前搵到施巴用，用完感覺好乾，但對頭皮真係有用，用到宜家"},{"pid":"ce87fb52e6a87a114012c0bf57d6dc9dc54a0edf","tid":621152,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:02:07.000Z","msg":"一定係睇左醫生先，皮膚有問題先會咁<br />\n我自己都係"},{"pid":"5d3f82fad7e1876a085e8f546ef24402e12bf060","tid":621152,"uid":136242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:07:15.000Z","msg":"我一路都無問題，但上個月去完剪頭髮就一直有勁多頭皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知關唔關啲剪髮工具事"},{"pid":"9b675ce93fae828b09412d203c704bdf3cbb6c9e","tid":621152,"uid":24641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:08:44.000Z","msg":"認真我細個返學都係咁<br />\n比人歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後尾聽人講轉左施巴好返好多但都仲有少少<br />\n而家轉左瀟灑洗頭水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一乾二淨"},{"pid":"388f8297d029c4b5f1ab780be7ffdc04b98d0d22","tid":621152,"uid":148454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:10:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30996c148650f5eee47330af86bef10b13723fd5","tid":621152,"uid":17545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:14:04.000Z","msg":"嚴重嘅話睇皮膚科醫生最好 有抗真菌洗頭水同抗真菌口服藥 食完之後調理身體睇中醫 脂漏性皮膚炎係不治之症 只可以減少強度同密度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3343518e01cb9c5e05cad036d9e37039c79037d","tid":621152,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:18:29.000Z","msg":"話說上面支野係咪真係有用＿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  想比呀哥試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢又係勁多頭皮"},{"pid":"3d4eb231c811008b71ae93907f8dad09303d5c89","tid":621152,"uid":63491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:20:14.000Z","msg":"之前用賴屎佬nizoral, 不過宜家貴左好多，未試過Selsun，上網睇好似都ok"},{"pid":"fbe9cb3fa54f7bf5cc8d38e9449da5c330bb9ad6","tid":621152,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:23:21.000Z","msg":"自問<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"234e4e2743e5b0804c3f0a8b75d97ceba0463d8d","tid":621152,"uid":17746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:25:13.000Z","msg":"用啲天然啲嘅洗頭水<br />\n間唔中先用深層清潔嘅洗頭水洗"},{"pid":"5c5f46103225ad5e88f26cb853630854a8d3ad0a","tid":621152,"uid":143757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedB