":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:39:59.000Z","msg":"強烈建議用Selsun Super<br />\n但記住跟足個包裝上面嘅方法用<br />\n如果唔係藥效唔到<br />\n<br />\n我成日推介俾病人用，反應都幾好<br />\n我自己有脂漏性皮炎，用普通Selsun Blue唔掂，但Selsun Super 我用一、兩次就keep到成幾個星期 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c991b9cb3d760d59d6ebfdc7c036bbefca52bb","tid":621152,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"89b4d583031e443a61ddd46a534f985eaab5fbea","tid":621152,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ab9aa6455e37e418ea23529d910302ab8c89916","tid":621152,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"ccec7b19477b2d7865f4c39462257244403111ac","tid":621152,"uid":52576,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:12:58.000Z","msg":"呢個真係好有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:16:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/22787269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F22787269&d=dkkLZikCC5jk9TNU3iTsbDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=39d98e04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/22787269</a><br />\n<br />\n长期使用复方酮康唑发用洗剂会有什么后果？<br />\n<br />\n好似有類固醇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:54:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母殘體狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:43:22.000Z","msg":"你老母俾狗屌阿<br />\n<br />\n好心SHARE俾大家知 唔好亂用咋"},{"pid":"8f75b7d84aee6f9feed2d54a318806afce72c837","tid":621152,"uid":31613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d87bb8eede2d5b76c57cccd4c9213989719d4f2a","tid":621152,"uid":61050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d40e69664d74c7039e4a78877dce0203054b8eef","tid":621152,"uid":31613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T08:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/08/163557_3f717b78cef56b0deb1ac91da0a2ffef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.